sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API
    participant Database
    participant Cache
    
    Client->>+API: GET /user/123
    
    API->>+Cache: Check cache
    Cache-->>-API: Cache miss
    
    API->>+Database: SELECT * FROM users WHERE id=123
    Database-->>-API: User data
    
    API->>Cache: Store in cache
    
    API-->>-Client: 200 OK + User data
    
    Note over Client,Cache: Subsequent request
    
    Client->>+API: GET /user/123
    API->>+Cache: Check cache
    Cache-->>-API: Cache hit
    API-->>-Client: 200 OK + User data (cached)
